  "content": [
    {
      "chapterUid": 7,
      "chapterTitle": "反思性",
      "items": [
        {
          "type": "highlight",
          "bookmarkId": "24019444_7_1548-1664",
          "range": "1548-1664",
          "rangeStart": 1548,
          "rangeEnd": 1664,
          "markText": "第三种，也是他最重视的是学术偏见，学究偏见（intellectualist bias）。这是指，学者将现实世界建构成一个有待被解释的学术图像，以一大套预设的理论、方法、原则、词汇来探索描述它，而忘了现实世界中有许多待解决的具体问题。",
          "colorStyle": 3,
          "colorLabel": "",
          "createTime": 1745130837,
          "createTimeFormatted": "2025-04-20 14:33:57",
          "chapterUid": 7,
          "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=24019444&chapterUid=7&rangeStart=1548&rangeEnd=1664",
          "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/4d732dd0716e81f44d7b743?chapterUid=7&rangeStart=1548&rangeEnd=1664"
        },
        {
          "type": "highlight",
          "bookmarkId": "24019444_7_2002-2087",
          "range": "2002-2087",
          "rangeStart": 2002,
          "rangeEnd": 2087,
          "markText": "我们每个人的社会出身背景，我们在此社会中的位置，以及由学术知识通过社会教育转化而成的“常识”，都是一层层的帷幕，或脚底的皮茧，屏障着我们对世间一切人、事、物的感触与认知。",
          "colorStyle": 2,
          "colorLabel": "",
          "createTime": 1745120853,
          "createTimeFormatted": "2025-04-20 11:47:33",
          "chapterUid": 7,
          "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=24019444&chapterUid=7&rangeStart=2002&rangeEnd=2087",
          "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/4d732dd0716e81f44d7b743?chapterUid=7&rangeStart=2002&rangeEnd=2087"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "chapterTitle": "历史与“历史”",
      "items": [
        {
          "type": "highlight",
          "bookmarkId": "24019444_6_1034-1097",
          "range": "1034-1097",
          "rangeStart": 1034,
          "rangeEnd": 1097,
          "markText": "所以，并不只是历史事实造成“现在”，而应是历史事实造成部分人掌握社会权力及历史记忆，历史记忆让人们生活在“现在”之社会现实中。",
          "colorStyle": 2,
          "colorLabel": "",
          "createTime": 1745120839,
